##
## Abstract:
##   Initialization file ~/.inputrc implements run-time configuration for the Readline library. It is interpreted whenever a
## program using the Readline library starts up.
##
## Details:
##   None.
##
## References:
## - GNU Readline Library
##   --> http://tiswww.case.edu/php/chet/readline/readline.html
## - stty(1) man page
##   --> $ man stty
